body:
Bumps [c-toxcore](https://github.com/TokTok/c-toxcore) from `f904179` to `d369c93`.
Commits
  • d369c93 chore: Fix Emscripten build failing with no host specified
  • 51b24d1 chore: Run CompCert on the stable branch of libsodium
  • cab1f7d chore: Update WineHQ's apt key hash
  • 102a1fa chore: Fix -Werror=maybe-uninitialized in a test
  • cc9515d chore: Fix cpplint failing to install
  • 3485b5f chore: Disable -Wswitch-default and -Wunsafe-buffer-usage
  • 719041e chore: Fix Circle CI failing on a missing clang lib
  • 5344d7f fix: Memory leak in the bootstrap daemon
  • fa20168 cleanup: Remove useless if clause
  • 7572888 chore: Fix GitHub actions deprecation warnings
